### Home
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts

### Get one contact
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/69fff6c4c970bb36b75d4710

### Create a new contact
POST http://localhost:3000/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alvaro",
  "lastName": "Nunez",
  "email": "anunez@email.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Blue",
  "birthday": "2004-05-10"
}

### Update a contact
PUT http://localhost:3000/contacts/69fff75fc970bb36b75d4711
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alvaro",
  "lastName": "Nunez",
  "email": "updated@email.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Red",
  "birthday": "2004-05-10"
}

### Delete a contact
DELETE http://localhost:3000/contacts/69fff6c4c970bb36b75d4710